exposedPasswordsReportDesc.message: Exposed passwords are passwords have been uncovered in known data breaches that were released publicly or sold on the dark web by hackers.

breachCheckUsernameEmail.message: Verifica cualquier nombre de usuario o dirección de correo electrónico que utilices.
